econd-level pages. "), mdx("h2", null, "04. Display Feedback"), mdx("p", null, "If the UI has changed state or if it\u2019s in the process of changing state, then the user needs to know about it \u2014 especially when the change was triggered by an action the user took.  "), mdx("p", null, "Feedback reduces uncertainty and frustration for the user, and preserves their confidence in the UI.  "), mdx("p", null, "A UI needs to show feedback for the following states:"), mdx("p", null, mdx("strong", {
